data.description:
Welcome to your dream home located in the vibrant City of Port Orange! Nestled in a beautifully landscaped setting, this home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with a bonus room ensuring comfort for the whole family. The spacious two-car garage provides ample storage for your toys and with no HOA restrictions, feel free to bring them all! The family room is adorned with a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Escape to the tranquility of the fenced-in backyard, creating a private oasis for outdoor enjoyment and entertaining. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, providing an ideal setting for entertainment. The living room, with its welcoming ambiance and easy flow, becomes the focal point for gatherings and socializing. Don't miss the opportunity to call this 
centrally located haven your home - it's a true charm waiting for you!
